OL,3,CUK Covid-19 Inquiry to examine impact
OL,4,Cof pandemic on healthcare
OL,6,FThe impact of the Covid pandemic on
OL,7,FNHS workers, patients and the delivery
OL,8,Fof healthcare is set to be examined by
OL,9,Fa public inquiry.
OL,11,FThe first public hearings of module
OL,12,Fthree of the UK Covid-19 Inquiry will
OL,13,Fbe held on Monday, with leaders from
OL,14,Fthe Health and Safety Executive and
OL,15,FUnison expected to give evidence this
OL,16,Fweek.
