OL,3,CUK Covid-19 Inquiry to examine impact
OL,4,Cof pandemic on healthcare
OL,6,FThis part of the inquiry is looking at
OL,7,Fthe governmental and societal response
OL,8,Fto Covid-19 by assessing the impact of
OL,9,Fthe pandemic on how NHS services were
OL,10,Fdelivered.
OL,12,FThis will include how managers led the
OL,13,Fpandemic response, the role of primary
OL,14,Fcare and GPs, NHS backlogs, and how
OL,15,Fthe vaccine programme was integrated.
OL,17,FThe diagnosis of long Covid and the
OL,18,Fsupport offered to those affected will
OL,19,Falso be examined.
