OL,6,FNicola Brook, solicitor at Broudie
OL,7,FJackson Canter, which represents more
OL,8,Fthan 7,000 families from the Covid-19
OL,9,FBereaved Families for Justice UK
OL,10,Fgroup, said: "This module of the
OL,11,Finquiry is one of the most important
OL,12,Fin understanding the true horrors of
OL,13,Fthe pandemic.
OL,15,F"It will reveal some of the most
OL,16,Fshocking details, distressing stories
OL,17,Fand outrageous scandals that took
OL,18,Fplace.
