OL,6,FIt said there was a "damaging absence
OL,7,Fof focus" on the measures and
OL,8,Finfrastructure that would be needed to
OL,9,Fdeal with a fast-spreading disease,
OL,10,Feven though a coronavirus outbreak at
OL,11,Fpandemic scale "was foreseeable".
OL,13,FChair Baroness Heather Hallett said
OL,14,Flessons must be learned because,
OL,15,Funless changes are made, the next
OL,16,Fpandemic will "bring with it immense
OL,17,Fsuffering and huge financial cost, and
OL,18,Fthe most vulnerable in society will
OL,19,Fsuffer the most".
